commentTextItems.html: Tiripano is Bowled and Afghan wins by 100 runs.

commentPostTextItems.html: Donald Tiripano is the Man of the Match and Sikandar Raza is the Man of the Series. Thanks for joining us for the ODI series. Please do join us back from Sunday for the first of the two four day games. Till then it's good night from all of us here
Good cricket from the Afghan and great batting from Richmond Mutumbami and Tymcen Maruma to take Zimbabwe to at least a good score.

milestones.description: Afghanistan's 100-run win against Zimbabwe is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 89-run win against Scotland
This is the lowest match aggregate (418) involving teams Zimbabwe & Afghanistan in ODIs
Samiullah Shinwari has scored 7 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for AFG breaking Mohammad Nabi's record
Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (37) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari
